= JNAeratorStudio =

JNAeratorStudio is a limited GUI front-end for JNAerator.

JNAerator is a tool that aims at industrializing the use of JNA and Rococoa.

JNA & Rococoa open wide the doors of C & Objective-C libraries to the Java world.
